ManageSingle:
Manage who can see stats on your profile page and who can see your single player game stats through other Social Club features. This setting does not control multiplayer stats and multiplayer history outside of your profile page.
NOTE: THIS CONTROL IS NOT YET LIVE FOR ALL GAMES.

PrivacyDetailsText: Use the settings on this page to manage certain profile information. Certain information will always be visible such as Crew membership, comments you make on somebody’s wall, and multiplayer data. For more details, check out our Privacy Policy.
